Install Docker DTool Box
Make sure you have Kitematic and Oracle VM Virtual Box manage

Copy docker-compose.yml at location C:\Program Files\Docker Toolbox
which as one grid, one firefox node and one chrome node
To start these nod use command:

docker-compose up -d


If you want to have 3 node of chrome browser use command
docker-compose scale nodechrome=3

If you want to have 3 node of firefox browser use command
docker-compose scale nodefirefox=2